  {
   "id": "short_greeting",
   "text": "Hello there! How are you doing today?"
  },
  {
   "id": "medium_news",
   "text": "Researchers announced a breakthrough in battery technology on Tuesday, claiming the new solid-state design can charge in under five minutes while retaining ninety percent capacity after a decade of daily use."
  },
  {
   "id": "long_narrative",
   "text": "The lighthouse keeper climbed the spiral staircase one last time, his lantern casting long shadows on the whitewashed walls. For forty-three years he had tended this light, through storms that shook the tower and calm nights when the beam swept over a glassy sea. Tomorrow the automation crew would arrive, and the old lamp room would belong to machines. He paused at the top, looking out at the horizon, and smiled at the memory of it all."
  },
  {
   "id": "numbers_dates",
   "text": "On March 3rd, 2026, the company reported quarterly revenue of $4,532,891.07, a 12.5% increase year over year, with 1,204 new customers across 38 countries."
  },
  {
   "id": "hard_words",
   "text": "The choir's ethereal rendition of the Worcestershire anthem left the colonel thoroughly nonplussed, though the subtle epitome of rural England remained indubitably picturesque."
  },
  {
   "id": "emotive",
   "text": "No way... you actually did it?! That's incredible! I honestly never thought we'd pull this off \u2014 wow, I'm speechless!"
  },
  {
   "id": "question_dialog",
   "text": "Are you sure this is the right address? The map says we should have arrived ten minutes ago, but I don't see any building here at all."
  },
  {
   "id": "technical",
   "text": "The API gateway routes each HTTPS request through a rate limiter before invoking the authentication microservice, which validates the JSON web token against the OAuth server's public key."
  }
